Welcome to the Lightning Shell! Read more at https://lightningshell.app

Recently added apps: "btc2fiat" (show Bitcoin price), "sc-im" (spreadsheet), "csview" (view CSV files), "links" (web browser), "perfectly-balanced" (LND node balancing). See more in-depth changes at https://lightningshell.app/history/

Use the /data directory to store files that you don't want to lose (configuration files, custom scripts, etc.)!

Run "man apps" to read about all available apps. Some apps have their own manual page as well, see for example "man sc-im".
Run "about" for more details about Lightning Shell.

